  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Early recovery assistance to monsoon flood affected population in Norther areas of Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will be implemented by Caritas Bangladesh Consortium under Emergency Response and Recovery Fund (ERRF) of the SHPR grants for the period 20th September 2020 &#x2013; 19th February 2021 .
This project is to address the early recovery needs and gaps to the affected people of monsoon flood 2020 in the northern part of the country (at Jamalpur and Sirajganj districts) in a coordinated way with local government representatives.</narrative>
  </description>
